quran[27]{c,v,t,f}:
  74,34,"Ó tún fi òwúrọ̀ nígbà tí ojúmọ́ bá mọ́ búra."
  74,35,"Dájúdájú (iná Saƙọr) ni ọ̀kan nínú (àwọn àdánwò) tó tóbi."
  74,36,"(Ó jẹ́) ìkìlọ̀ fún abara."
  75,31,"Kò kúkú gba òdodo gbọ́, kò sì kírun."
  75,32,"Ṣùgbọ́n ó pe òdodo ní irọ́. Ó sì kẹ̀yìn sí i."
  75,33,"Lẹ́yìn náà, ó lọ sí ọ̀dọ̀ àwọn ènìyàn rẹ̀, ó sì ń ṣe fáàrí."
  76,25,"Rántí orúkọ Olúwa rẹ ní àárọ̀ àti ní ìrọ̀lẹ́."
  76,26,"Àti ní òru, forí kanlẹ̀ fún Un. Kí o sì ṣàfọ̀mọ́ fún Un ní òru fún ìgbà pípẹ́."
  76,27,"Dájúdájú àwọn wọ̀nyí fẹ́ràn ayé. Wọ́n sì ń pa ọjọ́ tó wúwo tì sẹ́yìn wọn."
  77,22,"títí di gbèdéke àkókò kan tí A ti mọ̀ (ìyen, ọjọ́ ìbímọ)."
  77,23,"A sì ní ìkápá àti àyànmọ́ (lórí rẹ̀. Àwa sì ni) Olùkápá àti Olùpèbùbù ẹ̀dá tó dára."
  77,24,"Ègbé ni ní ọjọ́ yẹn fún àwọn olùpe-òdodo-nírọ́."
  78,19,"Wọ́n sì máa ṣí sánmọ̀ sílẹ̀. Ó sì máa di àwọn ìlẹ̀kùn."
  78,20,"Wọ́n máa mú àwọn àpáta rìn (bọ́ sí àyè mìíràn). Ó sì máa di ahúnpeéná."
  78,21,"Dájúdájú iná Jahanamọ, ó lúgọ sílẹ̀ lójú ọ̀nà."
  79,13,"Nítorí náà, igbe ẹyọ kan sì ni."
  79,14,"Nígbà náà ni wọn yóò bára wọn lórí ilẹ̀ gban̄sasa."
  79,15,"Ǹjẹ́ ọ̀rọ̀ (Ànábì) Mūsā ti dé ọ̀dọ̀ rẹ?"
  80,10,"ìwọ kò sì kọbi ara sí i."
  80,11,"Rárá (kò tọ́ bẹ́ẹ̀). Dájúdájú al-Ƙur’ān ni ìrántí."
  80,12,"Nítorí náà, ẹni tí ó bá fẹ́ kí ó rántí rẹ̀."
  81,7,"àti nígbà tí wọ́n bá so àwọn ẹ̀mí pọ̀ mọ́ra wọn, (ẹni rere pẹ̀lú ẹni rere, ẹni ibi pẹ̀lú ẹni ibi)"
  81,8,"àti nígbà tí ọmọbìnrin tí wọ́n bò mọ́lẹ̀ láàyè bá bèèrè pé"
  81,9,"ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ wo ni wọ́n pa òun fún,"
  82,1,"Nígbà tí sánmọ̀ bá fàya pẹ́rẹpẹ̀rẹ,1 {1}",footnotes:1:[Ẹ wo sūrah al-Baƙọrah ;  2:210, sūrah al-Furƙọ̄n; 25:25 àti Sūrah al-’Inṣiƙọ̄ƙ;  84:1-2]
  82,2,"àti nígbà tí àwọn ìràwọ̀ bá já bọ́ káàkiri,"
  82,3,"àti nígbà tí àwọn ibúdò bá ṣàn jára wọn,"